  "detailed_description": "In this VR game, you solve Sudoku in a physical space by placing the numbers into the slots of the board. It’s still the same game but with a different viewpoint.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Sudoku</h2>The objective is to fill a 9×9 grid with digits so that each column, each row, and each of the nine 3×3 subgrids that compose the grid contain all of the digits from 1 to 9.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Options</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157070/extras/119288b9cb8b30170b5bd52ed16afd6d.poster.avif?t=1670024326\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157070/extras/119288b9cb8b30170b5bd52ed16afd6d.webm?t=1670024326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157070/extras/119288b9cb8b30170b5bd52ed16afd6d.mp4?t=1670024326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>Choose your difficulty between Easy, Medium or Hard</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157070/extras/79bd65d8483c7a0ba5210be8a98851cd.poster.avif?t=1670024326\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157070/extras/79bd65d8483c7a0ba5210be8a98851cd.webm?t=1670024326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157070/extras/79bd65d8483c7a0ba5210be8a98851cd.mp4?t=1670024326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>Set the scale of the board for your height or for Seated mode</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Support</h2><br>This game is built exclusively for VR.",
  "about_the_game": "In this VR game, you solve Sudoku in a physical space by placing the numbers into the slots of the board. It’s still the same game but with a different viewpoint.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Sudoku</h2>The objective is to fill a 9×9 grid with digits so that each column, each row, and each of the nine 3×3 subgrids that compose the grid contain all of the digits from 1 to 9.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Options</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157070/extras/119288b9cb8b30170b5bd52ed16afd6d.poster.avif?t=1670024326\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157070/extras/119288b9cb8b30170b5bd52ed16afd6d.webm?t=1670024326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157070/extras/119288b9cb8b30170b5bd52ed16afd6d.mp4?t=1670024326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>Choose your difficulty between Easy, Medium or Hard</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157070/extras/79bd65d8483c7a0ba5210be8a98851cd.poster.avif?t=1670024326\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157070/extras/79bd65d8483c7a0ba5210be8a98851cd.webm?t=1670024326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1157070/extras/79bd65d8483c7a0ba5210be8a98851cd.mp4?t=1670024326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>Set the scale of the board for your height or for Seated mode</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Support</h2><br>This game is built exclusively for VR.",
